title: Let's Watch TV: Uncoupled
description:
Joe and Mama Fran chat about babies before getting into the Netflix show Uncoupled. The show stars Neil Patrick Harris as a middle aged gay man faced with the prospect of having to start dating again after his partner of 17 years leaves him without any warning.
